{"tid":2279342,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英資開始撤退？太古地產逾98億元售太古城中心第一座寫字樓全部權益","createTime":"2020-11-09T17:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T17:29:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9c260cb791a9ed08a38e32d416c0ad8921e84eaa","tid":2279342,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:01:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559136-20201109.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559136-20201109.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9yxZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=bbffa38e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559136-20201109.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=541b9f0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559136-20201109.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n太古地產就出售太古城中心第一座寫字樓全部權益訂立買賣協議，所售權益由股份及貸款組成，作價約98.45億元，可作調整，以現金及對價股份支付。而在簽約時，買方Rocha Land Limited已支付9.8億元。<br />\n<br />\n公司表示，將持有買方控股公司Raven Blue Limited股份不多於37%，從而代表太古城中心第一座寫字樓不超過37%的間接股本權益。<br />\n<br />\n根據買賣協議，買賣雙方分別有認購期權及認沽期權，買方擔保人可在行使期，收購太古所持有的買方控股公司股份，太古可要求買方擔保人按行使價收購。<br />\n<br />\n公告指，至6月底，有關物業權益估值約79.38億元，預料以法定基準計，出售將為太古地產帶來20.01億元的收益，以基本基準計則有54.71億元，用作一般營運資金。<br />\n<br />\n至於太古公司則獲得16.48億元的法定基準計收益，或44.86億元的基本基準計收益。"},{"pid":"acc6e7f45aeecb2b907b8736c9b611bdf98a9017","tid":2279342,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:10:53.000Z","msg":"上星期先有巴打講太古係唔知邊區掃緊地 賣office係要資金回籠<br />\n<br />\n老老豆豆扎根過百年 會唔會咁易放棄"},{"pid":"a949c2b0dd4da6d23fe278b3e5e2abc95e02cfb7","tid":2279342,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:11:45.000Z","msg":"大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313f53